name: The New Flex
description: I’m looking to take all the learnings since i've been in the space and create the $FLEX coin because I’ve become totally fascinated by how NFT’s are the new status symbol. My metaverse identity is @GinzaETH (on OpenSea and Twitter) but I’ve recently created a news website called The New Flex where i’m going to document all brands going in to the NFT space and sort of access and incentives they will offer to the community when buying the NFT. I see this as being the new flex, when it used to be an expensive watch or pair of sneakers, now it’s virtual collectibles that can be seen by millions. I think this is a fundamental shift in materialistic consumption and is only going to get bigger.   I'm the right person to launch this because I have spent the large part of my career in the comms industry as a brand strategist for advertising agencies so my lens of the world is always through brands and how they adapt and adopt new channels. I think the $FLEX coin could be huge and I would love to be able to make it happen with you guys. Audience benefits will include members only access to the Discord community. Listed name on a supporters thank you page. Pre-sale on drops. Voting rights on community decisions. In person merch, access to VIP real world events, a commemorative NFT for being a member, exclusive members only content eg newsletter.
